<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3">The iODBC Driver Manager</bridgehead>
<para>The iODBC Driver Manager is a platform-independent, open source implementation of Microsoft&#39;s ODBC Driver Manager.
 A runtime iODBC Driver Manager is bundled with each of OpenLink&#39;s non-Windows client drivers and iODBC SDKs.
 Driver Manager source code is also contained within iODBC SDKs.
</para></section></docbook>